data.description: Charming well maintained home not far from ISU. Kitchen was remodeled a few years ago and includes all appliances and granite counters. Microwave may not be in working condition. The living room has newer LVP flooring. Steel siding, vinyl windows, furnace and air conditioning done in about 2008. The roof was replaced in 2021. The main bedroom has a walk in closet and door to bathroom. There is a big family room in the basement, also a bedroom but it doesn't have an egress window. Small yard that is partly fenced. A carport and shed too.
